title: Big data takes aim at a big human problem

title_detail.value: Big data takes aim at a big human problem

summary: A scientist is part of an international team that's used new 'big data' analysis to achieve a major advance in understanding neurological disorders such as Epilepsy, Alzheimer's and Parkinson's disease.
